A man and his teenage son have been arrested after his son
shot and killed a fellow pupil at Denga Tshivase High School outside
Thohoyandou.On  Friday  the 16-year-old school pupil managed to get
hold of his father's firearm and brought it to school. He then shoot a fellow pupil aged 18, during an alleged
